0712_us_report_hsbc_laundering_scandal&h=507588e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/business/2016/07/160712_us_report_hsbc_laundering_scandal</a>"},{"pid":"ab0e2479c5a4ed02076777d0faf924891ab9022b","tid":1790583,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:22:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"322440529b039b8c237142794a03680a8abeaa45","tid":1790583,"uid":343134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:23:02.000Z","msg":"好計謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n匯豐曾經幫伊朗洗過黑錢有無source？"},{"pid":"3b8bba59a44b19a5b67886840e9cdf9108047da9","tid":1790583,"uid":253945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"322440529b039b8c237142794a03680a8abeaa45","tid":1790583,"uid":343134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:23:02.000Z","msg":"好計謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n匯豐曾經幫伊朗洗過黑錢有無source？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:24:18.000Z","msg":"睇上面BBC條LINK <br />\n<br />\n匯豐洗錢案<br />\n2012年 匯豐簽署的和解協議透露了洗錢案的細節，匯豐向來自伊朗、利比亞、蘇丹、緬甸以及古巴的客戶提供的服務違反了美國的制裁決議。<br />\n<br />\n匯豐向墨西哥的錫納羅亞販毒集團（Sinaloa）以及哥倫比亞的北河谷卡特爾（Cartel del Norte del Valle）販毒組織提供賬戶，洗錢金額高達近9億美元。<br />\n<br />\n這份和解協議承諾不對匯豐銀行或任何高管進行刑事起訴。<br />\n<br />\n如果受到刑事起訴，匯豐有可能在美國被撤銷銀行牌照。"},{"pid":"a65fec2a2a93ac7f89d970e123f8b09fc97c2ea4","tid":1790583,"uid":85292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:25:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0b06b04ce9dbf6158a8a42fcab5462bac5c35a4","tid":1790583,"uid":307398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:26:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5e9545cf8186ef4339c1aa85f62519c687bd59c7","tid":1790583,"uid":155598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:29:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e605073d6ea7a8fd11aa21f7c8ba71a2ffbf160","tid":1790583,"uid":55932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:29:36.0